241
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,919
And that is before
they hit the resale market.

242
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:17,240
And with huge artists starting to put
tickets on sale for summer shows,

243
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:19,480
